{"name": "frozenlist", "metadata": {"name": "frozenlist", "version": "1.3.1", "classifiers": ["Development Status :: 5 - Production/Stable", "Intended Audience :: Developers", "License :: OSI Approved :: Apache Software License", "Operating System :: MacOS :: MacOS X", "Operating System :: Microsoft :: Windows", "Operating System :: POSIX", "Programming Language :: Python", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.10", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.11", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.7", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.8", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.9"], "home_page": "https://github.com/aio-libs/frozenlist", "license": "Apache 2", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": [], "summary": "A list-like structure which implements collections.abc.MutableSequence", "upload_time": 1659514976}, "documentation": ["# frozenlist\n\n```{image} https://github.com/aio-libs/frozenlist/workflows/CI/badge.svg\n:alt: GitHub status for master branch\n:target: https://github.com/aio-libs/frozenlist/actions\n```\n\n```{image} https://codecov.io/gh/aio-libs/frozenlist/branch/master/graph/badge.svg\n:alt: codecov.io status for master branch\n:target: https://codecov.io/gh/aio-libs/frozenlist\n```\n\n```{image} https://badge.fury.io/py/frozenlist.svg\n:alt: Latest PyPI package version\n:target: https://pypi.org/project/frozenlist\n```\n\n```{image} https://readthedocs.org/projects/frozenlist/badge/?version=latest\n:alt: Latest Read The Docs\n:target: https://frozenlist.readthedocs.io/\n```\n\n```{image} https://img.shields.io/discourse/topics?server=https%3A%2F%2Faio-libs.discourse.group%2F\n:alt: Discourse group for io-libs\n:target: https://aio-libs.discourse.group/\n```\n\n```{image} https://badges.gitter.im/Join%20Chat.svg\n:alt: Chat on Gitter\n:target: https://gitter.im/aio-libs/Lobby\n```\n\n## Introduction\n\n`frozenlist.FrozenList` is a list-like structure which implements\n`collections.abc.MutableSequence`. The list is *mutable* until `FrozenList.freeze`\nis called, after which list modifications raise `RuntimeError`:\n\n```\n>>> from frozenlist import FrozenList\n>>> fl = FrozenList([17, 42])\n>>> fl.append('spam')\n>>> fl.append('Vikings')\n>>> fl\n<FrozenList(frozen=False, [17, 42, 'spam', 'Vikings'])>\n>>> fl.freeze()\n>>> fl\n<FrozenList(frozen=True, [17, 42, 'spam', 'Vikings'])>\n>>> fl.frozen\nTrue\n>>> fl.append(\"Monty\")\nTraceback (most recent call last):\n  File \"<stdin>\", line 1, in <module>\n  File \"frozenlist/_frozenlist.pyx\", line 97, in frozenlist._frozenlist.FrozenList.append\n    self._check_frozen()\n  File \"frozenlist/_frozenlist.pyx\", line 19, in frozenlist._frozenlist.FrozenList._check_frozen\n    raise RuntimeError(\"Cannot modify frozen list.\")\nRuntimeError: Cannot modify frozen list.\n```\n\nFrozenList is also hashable, but only when frozen. Otherwise it also throws a RuntimeError:\n\n```\n>>> fl = FrozenList([17, 42, 'spam'])\n>>> hash(fl)\nTraceback (most recent call last):\n  File \"<stdin>\", line 1, in <module>\n  File \"frozenlist/_frozenlist.pyx\", line 111, in frozenlist._frozenlist.FrozenList.__hash__\n    raise RuntimeError(\"Cannot hash unfrozen list.\")\nRuntimeError: Cannot hash unfrozen list.\n>>> fl.freeze()\n>>> hash(fl)\n3713081631934410656\n>>> dictionary = {fl: 'Vikings'} # frozen fl can be a dict key\n>>> dictionary\n{<FrozenList(frozen=True, [1, 2])>: 'Vikings'}\n```\n\n### Installation\n\n```\n$ pip install frozenlist\n```\n\nThe library requires Python 3.6 or newer.\n\n## Documentation\n\n<https://frozenlist.readthedocs.io/>\n\n## Communication channels\n\n*aio-libs discourse group*: <https://aio-libs.discourse.group>\n\nFeel free to post your questions and ideas here.\n\n*gitter chat* <https://gitter.im/aio-libs/Lobby>\n\n## Requirements\n\n- Python >= 3.6\n\n## License\n\n`frozenlist` is offered under the Apache 2 license.\n\n## Source code\n\nThe project is hosted on [GitHub]\n\nPlease file an issue in the [bug tracker](https://github.com/aio-libs/frozenlist/issues) if you have found a bug\nor have some suggestions to improve the library.\n\n[github]: https://github.com/aio-libs/frozenlist\n"], "modules": [{"name": "tests.conftest", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "setup", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "setup.NO_EXTENSIONS", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "setup.ext_modules", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "setup.ext_modules", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "frozenlist", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "frozenlist.__version__", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "frozenlist.NO_EXTENSIONS", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "frozenlist.PyFrozenList", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "frozenlist.FrozenList", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [{"name": "frozenlist.FrozenList", "bases": ["MutableSequence"], "methods": [{"name": "frozenlist.FrozenList.__class_getitem__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "cls", "type": {"name": "Type", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Type", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "FrozenList", "xref": {"fqname": "frozenlist.FrozenList", "project": null}, "params": null}]}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "Type", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Type", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "FrozenList", "xref": {"fqname": "frozenlist.FrozenList", "project": null}, "params": null}]}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "frozenlist.FrozenList.__init__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "items", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "frozenlist.FrozenList.frozen", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "frozenlist.F